# Script Composer SDK — Project Conventions

- This repo is a **pnpm workspace**: `packages/*` (SDK) and `examples/*` (apps). Root has no application source, only workspace scripts and config.
- **Build and test from root**: `pnpm build`, `pnpm test`. Do not assume running build/test from a subpackage is the default; prefer root for full workspace consistency.
- **Terminology**: "Script Composer" and "AptosScriptComposer" refer to the SDK. "Multi-agent" here means **Aptos multi-signer or fee-payer transactions**, not AI/LLM agents. Use "multi-signer" or "fee payer" when disambiguation is needed.
- For project overview, structure, and commands, see [AGENTS.md](/AGENTS.md) at repo root.
